      "settings": {
        "richtext_1": "<p><em>Venty was born from a simple frustration: the market was flooded with cheaply made, uninspired products that break easily and lack real innovation. We saw a race to the bottom<\/em><\/p><p><em>where quality was sacrificed for price, and user experience was an afterthought. We knew there had to be a better way.<\/em><br\/><\/p><h6><strong>Matthew Slack, Venty CEO<\/strong><\/h6>",
        "richtext_2": "<p>At Venty, we’re passionate about creating beautifully designed, intuitive products that enhance everyday life. We obsess over the details—from how something feels in your hand to how seamlessly it fits into your lifestyle. We invest heavily in research and development because we believe that great design starts with a deep understanding of real-world needs.<\/p><p>We don’t cut corners. We don’t chase trends. And we never release a product unless we’re genuinely proud of it.<\/p><p>Our goal is simple: to set a new standard for what portable comfort and cooling can be. Whether you're camping off-grid, working remotely, or just enjoying your backyard, we’re here to bring you smart, reliable products that deliver—again and again.<\/p><p>Welcome to Venty. Design-forward. Innovation-driven. Built to last.<\/p><p><strong>Venty<\/strong><br\/>6900 Westcliff Dr. Ste 503 <br\/>Las Vegas, NV 89145<\/p>",
